"And if there is none. make one. then."

268
00:17:02.563 --> 00:17:03.606
- [laughing]
- Yeah.

269
00:17:03.689 --> 00:17:05.650
[Yun-seok]
What's with this guy? Every time...

270
00:17:05.733 --> 00:17:08.194
- [Boksoon sighs]
