349
00:20:38.446 --> 00:20:43.159
Those rules were just a way for MK
to monopolize the industry. Were they not?

350
00:20:43.242 --> 00:20:45.122
Think about it.
Other than Sergeant Shin's crew.

351
00:20:45.161 --> 00:20:47.163
