Huh?

470
00:26:40.432 --> 00:26:42.192
I'm not giving it to you.
You'll pay me back.

471
00:26:42.267 --> 00:26:44.895
Don't need it.
I've already taken care of it.

472
00:26:45.479 --> 00:26:46.479
You what?

473
00:26:47.022 --> 00:26:48.357
