513
00:28:49.645 --> 00:28:51.104
Gwanggaeto the Great.

514
00:28:51.188 --> 00:28:53.482
Eulji Mundeok. Kim Gu. An Jung-guen...

515
00:28:53.565 --> 00:28:55.525
