Uh. here keep it like this.

2082
02:10:12.013 --> 02:10:13.347
It's pretty stuffy.

2083
02:10:39.915 --> 02:10:41.042
[scoffs]

2084
02:10:49.633 --> 02:10:51.552
[Boksoon whimpers]

2085
02:10:57.433 --> 02:10:59.435
